Class SwitchPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toDex.instructions.AbstractInsn

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Insn
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PackedSwitchPayload, SparseSwitchPayload
    public abstract class SwitchPayload
extends AbstractPayload
    The payload for switch instructions, usually placed at the end of a method. This is where the jump targets are stored.

    Note that this is an InsnWithOffset with multiple offsets.
